author: mmarinschek
msg: made calling of several javascript functions dependent on if they are actually present. Added source section to the poms. Default message now also prints the message of the causes of an exception.

author: danj
msg: Permanent fix for MUSE-30: Our use of Axis2's EndpointReference.toOM() was causing the problem - the
1.0 version (and later snapshot I had) had a bug that put the parameters in metadata. If you read
the parameters from EndpointReference.geAllReferenceParameters(), the values are all there. There
has been a recent fix to toOM() that is available in the nightly snapshots, but I just made the
change to iterate over the values and now it should work against even the 1.0 codebase.
